metadata.name: Fire Inside
metadata.description:
A visual representation of my passion for life and art, this 1/1 artwork was born by the (your)self open collaboration project by artist Rik Oostenbroek. The earth constrains our physical bodies, but our thoughts and spirit transcend those bounds.
